# PennyPlay — Supabase wiring (optional)
#
# Leave these unset to run in local demo mode (all data stays on this device).
# To connect a real Supabase backend:
#   1. Create a project at https://supabase.com (or `supabase projects create`)
#   2. Apply the migrations in supabase/migrations/ (`supabase db push`)
#   3. Deploy the edge function (`supabase functions deploy award-xp`)
#   4. Copy this file to .env and fill in the values from your project's API settings

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
